      <body>
         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Munich, 2 March 1872 ¶ Baron Ferdinand von Mueller Director of the botanical Garden ¶ Melbourne, Australia. ¶  ¶ Attention drawn to you by Professor Doctor Eichler, Graz, the undersigned takes the lib...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">72.03.02</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">From Richard Jaeger</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">VPRS 5831/P0/4, p. 173, Correspondence inwards, Miscellaneous letters, Melbourne Public Library, Public Record Office Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">München 2ter Maerz 1872</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Herrn Baron Ferdinand von Müller Direktor des botanischen Gartens</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Melbourne (Australien)</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Der Unterzeichnete, von Herrn Professor Dr Eichler Graz auf Sie aufmerksam gemachte gestattet sich hiermit, Ihnen ein in seinem Besitz befindliches Exemplar von <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Fasc 1-50</hi>
               </seg> (soweit zum Jahre 1871 erschienen) von <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Marteus Flora Brasiliensis Enumeratio Plantarum in Brasilia Ladenpreis R. 483-, vollständig und neu zu R. 380- baar und Verpackung</hi>
               </seg> zu offeriren.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Der billige Preis dieses in seiner Art einzig dastehenden Werkes dürfte Ihnen vielleicht Veranlassung geben, dasselbe zur Anschaffung für die Bibliothek zu empfehlen.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Gefälliger Rückantwort gerne entgegensehend, zeichnet</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Hochachtungsvoll</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Rich. Jaeger</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Gabelsbergerstrasse 50/I (München Bayern)</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">Munich, 2 March 1872</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Baron Ferdinand von Mueller Director of the botanical Garden</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Melbourne, Australia.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Attention drawn to you by Professor Doctor Eichler, Graz, the undersigned takes the liberty herewith of offering you a copy in his possession of <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">fascicles 1-50</hi>
               </seg> (so far published to 1871) of <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Marteus</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                     <p rend="Footnote"
                        style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                        <seg style="">
                           <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>i.e. Martius.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> </seg>
               <seg style="font-style: italic; ">
                  <hi rend="underline">Flora Brasiliensis Enumeratio Plantarum in Brasilia</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">retail price R 483, complete and new at R 380 cash and packing</hi>
               </seg>.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>The cheap price of this work, unique of its kind, may perhaps cause you to recommend it for purchase for the library.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Looking forward to your kind answer, signs<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">MS annotation: '£57.0.0'. M forwarded this letter to Augustus Tulk (see M to A. Tulk, 5 May 1872), who noted that the price was 'Too dear'. A further annotation reads: 'Colored Plates Price new £40'.</p>
               </note>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">most respectfully</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Richard Jaeger</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Gabelsbergerstrasse 50/I (Munich, Bavaria).</p>
         </div>
